NHANCED BRUSHES</h2>Pressure, smoothness and transparency based brush with full sensitivity control.<br>\"Hook\" brush for creating guided strokes easily and intuitively.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/5efc0c5e4788c794f86c19126783c3e5.poster.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/5efc0c5e4788c794f86c19126783c3e5.webm?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/5efc0c5e4788c794f86c19126783c3e5.mp4?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ANATOMICALLY ACCURATE MODELS</h2>2 new anatomically accurate models added with color groups for sets of muscles.<br>Pose the new male and female models with an accurate deformations and proportions<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/a933d1f758c9bc9d649aabfdd6464e71.poster.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/a933d1f758c9bc9d649aabfdd6464e71.webm?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/a933d1f758c9bc9d649aabfdd6464e71.mp4?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POSE AND DRAW</h2>Have you ever wanted a professional model who would perform a variety of poses to make drawing animation, illustrations, and sketching easier? By manipulating the 3D model on the screen, you can create poses seen in everyday life, sports, martial arts, etc., and then draw on a seperate layer for getting the right proportions and perspective.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/3697d5473a858f4aa967ee770772490c.poster.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/3697d5473a858f4aa967ee770772490c.webm?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/3697d5473a858f4aa967ee770772490c.mp4?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IMPORT 3D MESHES</h2>Add background details easily by importing in .OBJ files and .FBX files into the 3D layer and merge it seamlessly into the main 2D scene.<br>Use the inbuilt models of 3d cities, vehicles, trees,interiors and hundreds of props  to add complexity to your compositions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/04040b906f2c4cf11af77205882c2a54.poster.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/04040b906f2c4cf11af77205882c2a54.webm?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/04040b906f2c4cf11af77205882c2a54.mp4?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PRECISE BRUSH CONTROL</h2>Easily control brush curves,smoothness and thick/thin with 3 simple controls.<br>\"Catch up\" controls on the brush allows precise drawing curve control with beautiful lines.<br>Pressure sensitivity and Windows Ink compatibility fully supported on Wacom/Huion/Xppen tablets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/705e35444882f956180734c35ba35a23.poster.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/705e35444882f956180734c35ba35a23.webm?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/705e35444882f956180734c35ba35a23.mp4?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIFFERENT VISUAL STYLES</h2>Switch between grayscale,black white outline  and grayscale toon shading in the 3D scene<br>Snapshot and integrate 3D scenes seamlessly into a 2D layer for an seamless 2d/3d look.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/0e96dc5497944619f016d9fbc1b3cb32.poster.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/0e96dc5497944619f016d9fbc1b3cb32.webm?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/0e96dc5497944619f016d9fbc1b3cb32.mp4?t=1762432867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2>*Seamlessy add 2d layers so that you can paint non-destructively with a pen tablet w/ pressure control.<br><br>*Save,load and export 3D poses for all 7 characters bundled ranging from realistic male to anime girl.<br><br>*An innovative hand editor allows users to get precise hand poses whilst intuitive camera controls lets users easily setup complex 3D scenes.<br><br>*Export out layers as .PNG files ,so users can preserve details in layers and making color separation easy.<br><br>*Import in external 3D meshes using the .OBJ format or .FBX formats to easily add background details.FBX animations can be scrubbed frame by frame.<br><br>*Hundreds of  models of buildings, cities ,vehicles, trees, furniture, interior scenes, crowds and geometric primitives  are bundled in the app for fast layouts.<br><br>*Intuitive controllers and transform manipulators allows users to easily pose their characters in 3d space.<br><br>*Layer control allows users to add multiple transparent 2d layers on the existing 3d layer.<br><br>*You can load in a total of 7 different characters  ranging from normal proportions to stylized anime in order to get the right body shape and style.<br><br>*Control lighting and shading modes so you can switch between looks like toon shaded and black/white noir easily.<br><br>*Smooth brush and pressure sliders with catch up functionality makes inking easy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXAMPLE SCENES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/1c6c3002721e93436309e770d17ddbfe.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=220 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/3403c6e145dc1fc5aebdc453fecd8e6d.avif?t=1762432867\" width=612 height=220 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/e70c9f9c03f3c56ec70f96c8425f4ead.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=220 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/2c64fe85699e01339c574b48c9e50c14.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=220 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810590/extras/b0eb33c7f980c858c6a67729ff5047b6.avif?t=1762432867\" width=640 height=220 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src